{"tid":797034,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"（蓋清入）劉德華演唱會取消售票處售票 歌迷買飛只得3個途徑","createTime":"2018-08-28T07:57:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T16:51:03.000Z","uid":36497,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1949f3ce0271f7bcf380dcc365cee138ead6b98f","tid":797034,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T07:57:59.000Z","msg":"劉德華將於今年12月舉行20場跨年演唱會，門票將於9月初公開發售，惟日前有粉絲通宵排隊買飛時被斬傷。為免再有歌迷受傷及杜絕黃牛黨，華仔所屬公司與康文署及警方協商後，以「基於保障市民的人身安全及維持公眾治安等重要考慮」，決定取消售票處售票，歌迷只可透過城市售票網網頁、信用卡電話購票及流動應用程式My URBTIX這3種方法購票，而且每人每次限購最多4張門票。<br />\n<br />\nSOURCE：<a href=\"https://ol.mingpao.com/php/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1535441610164&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=20180828\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fphp%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1535441610164%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20180828&d=VNmlqQ1PE7hT5e2WvJGzcdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=66606cdd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fphp%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1535441610164%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20180828&h=40e3c6dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://ol.mingpao.com/php/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1535441610164&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=20180828</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地南亞人＋炒賣師又沒得賺了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1d995b004424e0aaff3d980c91ed1decab95ce7","tid":797034,"uid":64095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T07:58:48.000Z","msg":"我有飛 要既話PM我"},{"pid":"ca24da0337da36b0adddd57d1e953e0503efc7cc","tid":797034,"uid":36497,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1d995b004424e0aaff3d980c91ed1decab95ce7","tid":797034,"uid":64095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T07:58:48.000Z","msg":"我有飛 要既話PM我"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T07:59:39.000Z","msg":"老豆都無飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6df1fcaa865307d1d3bdc21804188d6dca84f759","tid":797034,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":1,"s